# The `FoldingSetVector` Class Template Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/foldingsetvector">FoldingSetVector</a> - This template class combines a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/foldingset">FoldingSet</a> and a vector to provide the interface of <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/foldingset">FoldingSet</a> but with deterministic iteration order based on the insertion order. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/foldingsetvector">FoldingSetVector</a> - This template class combines a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/foldingset">FoldingSet</a> and a vector to provide the interface of <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/foldingset">FoldingSet</a> but with deterministic iteration order based on the insertion order.

T must be a subclass of <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a368e3de8ea854f34bc97c21a64d6a164">FoldingSetNode</a> and implement a Profile function.

Definition at line 647 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/foldingset-h">FoldingSet.h</a>.
